Package: dpll-mgr
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Advanced PTP Timing Synchronization Manager
 dpll-mgr is a timing synchronization manager for Intel platforms with
 DPLL hardware support. It coordinates PTP clock recovery, DPLL lock
 management, gearshift phase alignment, and GNSS reference monitoring
 for precision timing applications.
